high_descs: Turn left and walk to the corner, then turn left and walk to the counter on the other side of the room.
Take the cup from the coffee maker.
Turn right and face the stove then look up.
Put the cup in the microwave and heat it for five seconds, then take it out.
Turn left and face the counter.
Put the cup back in the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Heat a cup in the microwave.

high_descs: head over to the coffee maker
grab the cup out of the coffee maker
turn right to face the microwave above the stove
put the cup inside the microwave and microwave it, then take it back out
bring the cup back over to the coffee maker
place the cup in the area underneath the spout of the coffee maker
anns.task_desc: get a hot cup under the coffee maker

high_descs: Turn to your left and go around the island to the counter.
Pick up the coffee cup in the coffee maker.
Carry the cup to the microwave above the stove.
Microwave the cup and take it out.
Bring the cup to the coffee maker.
Put the cup in the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Heat the cup for the coffee maker.
